@startuml
title Context View - FFmpeg GUI Use Cases

actor User

rectangle "FFmpeg GUI Application" {
    usecase "Select Input File" as UC1
    usecase "Choose Output Format" as UC2
    usecase "Convert File" as UC3
    usecase "View Conversion Logs" as UC4
    usecase "View Error Message" as UC5
}

User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4

UC3 --> UC5 : if conversion fails


@enduml
